"kami memposting tutorial tentang cara menggunakan berbagai fitur plugin."

#: app/Strings.php:298
msgid ""
"How can I create a table from an imported XLSX file in google spreadsheets?"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana cara membuat tabel dari file XLSX yang diimpor di google "
"spreadsheets?"

#: app/Strings.php:300
msgid ""
"Make sure to import the XLSX file into Google Spreadsheets in the following "
"ways. Create a new blank spreadsheet, then navigate to `<span class='date-"
"format'><code> File > Import > Upload</code></span>` Drag the XLSX files to "
"import. Then share the spreadsheets from 'General Access'. Please visit our "
"<a target='_blank' href='https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLd6WEu38CQSyY-1rzShSfsHn4ZVmiGNLP'>YouTube playlist</a>, where we post "
"tutorials on how you can use XLSX file imported in google spreadsheets."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan untuk mengimpor file XLSX ke Google Spreadsheets dengan cara "
"berikut. Buat spreadsheet kosong baru, lalu navigasi ke `<span class='date-"
"format'><code> File > Import > Upload</code></span>` Seret file XLSX untuk "
"diimpor. Kemudian bagikan spreadsheet dari 'General Access'. Silakan "
"kunjungi <a target='_blank' href='https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLd6WEu38CQSyY-1rzShSfsHn4ZVmiGNLP'>playlist YouTube</a> kami, di mana "
"kami memposting tutorial tentang cara menggunakan file XLSX yang diimpor di "
"google spreadsheets."

